node.text: Video dedicated for my baby girl Wolfie, I hope you will enjoy watching it when you get older so you can remember & relive those amazing moments we had together (everytime i think of the fact babies forget when they’re babies as they grow it makes me cry cause I cannot believe those moments are soooo intense for me but she won’t remember🥺) hope this video will help hihi ❤️ As you can see, you were always the most intelligent, beautiful & incredible girl, you certainly still are today (yes talking to you Wolfie of the future haha) You make everyday the most beautiful day of my life again & again & again. You have this super power of bringing everyone together & making everyone smile on a daily basis 💕 i love you mi amor , the most loved baby on the planet 🍉

node.text:
Currently sitting on the train, I made a q/a on my stories & I had so many questions about when I am going to stop breastfeeding & i was even told that Wolfie is too old and I should stop. First thing I want to make clear : she is not too old at all, the longest you can breastfeed your baby the best it is 🤱🏼 Breastfeeding is one of the best gifts you can do for your loved one, alot of people have to stop earlier because of many different reasons but mostly because they have to go back to work & it becomes veryyy complicated or impossible. I am lucky enough to have a job/lifestyle that allows me to be with her 24/7 (i have this job because of you so : THANK YOU!) & i don’t plan on stopping breastfeeding it’s not even something that crosses my mind at this point.. why would I want to give her milk processed from cows & made for baby cows while I have my own milk that was specially prepared for her with all the  anti bodies she needs (btw no shades to cow milk, I drink it too but even tho I drink it I still find it special that we are the only “animal” drinking milk coming from another animal 😅) 
To conclude, I just think our breastfeeding journey comes from our own personal choices / preferences / obligations / body , no body experience it the same way, i just consider myself lucky to be able to do it for so long, I’ll still breastfeed till Wolfie no longer wants to, if she’s 6 years old, she’ll be 6 years old if she’s 2, she’ll be 2 ! We’re not stressing about it, just enjoying the current moment as it is our little special time of the day everyday 🥰

node.text: Her first time in Europe 🥺💕 so very happy to be experiencing her first time in Spain 🇪🇸 we currently have absolutely no plans haha We only booked our flights & .. that’s it ! So time to let us know WHAT DO WE ABSOLUUUUTELY NEED TO SEE ? ✨ Since we really wanted to come here but knew we couldn’t rent a car (cause i couldn’t get my international liscence on time) we decided to do a “common transportation trip” which means : we didn’t bring Wolfie’s car seat cause we didn’t want to have a to bring it everywhere so we can only travel by bus or train while we’re here 🚂 I’ve done this kinda trip twice in the past in Italy, after talking to locals, they told me transportation is very similar & it’ll be easy to see the principal only this way … so we’re now trying it ! We have no plans cayse we’ll see if it’s really easy or not & we’ll go day by day in case there is a spot we love too much ✨ we’re just not stressed about life right now, it is vacation time & my Sagittarius self can only be excited about this new adventure 🌈 i thought this way of traveling was going to be over for me when I have Wolfie but actually no, she doesn’t care if we don’t know where we are sleeping tonight, she wouldn’t even know either way 😅 nothing is certain except that every night she’ll have a bed & everyday she’ll eat good european food .. it can’t go wrong (could it ?😂)

Our inventory is VERY LIMITED for the sale 🤞🏽 international shipping 🌍 love love 🦋

node.text: Family tourist day to celebrate our reunion 🐠 Today was my happiest day in a long time (note: I said happiest, cause I’m always very happy but today was extra extra mega happy) ☀️ Since I had Wolfie in my life, I’m the happiest i’ve ever been but I think i can say the same about Christo now, we’ve been away for so long and it made me realize how much he counts for me (& for Wolfie) 🌈 it felt so weird when we saw each other again (those who saw the video will understand haha) it was like we didn’t know each other even tho we spent months together 24/7 & even when he was gone we would facetime every single day for 2 months but… yea the feeling to see each other again was so weird, it was like i had never met him, he felt kinda “not real” for me, maybe it was too beautiful to be true ?? But finally my brain processed it & after only 15 minutes it was like he never left 💕 we’re so happy to be back together, we don’t know for how long but i’ll do my best to never be away for that long again 🥺 we like you @c.r.iscontreras 🥰

node.text:
Matcha & palm trees, all i’m wishing for right now 😋🌴 I can’t stop thinking about going back to Costa Rica soon, I’m too excited (also enjoying my time here at the same time, i’m just happy in general with my life so i’m not rushing haha) 🌈 there is 2 things I really like about Costa Rica that are visible in this pic : 1- I can walk almost anywhere with a bikini, they don’t care it’s “la pura vida” , people are not bothering with things that are not important ! Life is too short to get negative feelings from stupid things that don’t change anything in your life ( for example : most places I’d feel judge to walk in a bikini anywhere but in Costa.. not at all ! & there is so many other things like that.. let me convince you : in the area where I am I could bring my dogs to the restaurant 😍 LIFE GOALS JUST FOR THAT) & the second thing I really love that we can see in this photo is the food ! Since I got here I feel like it tastes so different, the food there is incredible, super natural i’d say, they often cook with what they have in their garden or just around & that’s something I really appreciate the veggies & fruits are so yummy 😋🪴 so, who wants to move with me ? ✈️ 
Oh & another thing i really appreciate there is my friend @daryaseafilms who takes the best photos on earth 🌍

node.text: PINCH ME !!!! After a crazy weekend, today we’ve just had a little reveal event for our next warehouse 💕 YES WE’RE BUILDING OUR OWN GIANT WAREHOUSE & IT’LL BE INCREDIBLE  I STILL CANNOT BELIEVE IT 😭 What does it mean ? More inventory & more launch & more items & just more more 🌈 actually it is already under construction & it’ll be ready in January but I had to keep the secret hihi 🥰 I remember when I started my business, I was 17 & it thought “oh it’ll be nice to have abit of side money while i’m at university” finally 6 years later look at where we are !! People always tell me “look at what you’ve built” “you’re so inspiring for entrepreneurs” , that’s super sweet but honestly if it was just me all alone Hoaka wouldn’t be here ! We’re all the family included in this adventure now, every members of the family is so important to our success (can I call it a success myself ??? Maybe yes just for today haha!!) & not only my family but also all of the Hoaka team, we’ve had girls working with us for up to 4 years , they’ve lived this adventure with us 🦋 & of course I want to mention all of you girls who have been supporting us in any way, by buying a bikini or sharing a giveaway, by posting with Hoaka or only liking our photos, honestly just all the love & support we get from the start is out of this world, thank you for trusting us 🌸 also a big thank you to everyone implicated in this project, there is not enough space here to thank everyone I wish to thank but ILY ALL … so ! Do you like it ?! 😍

node.text: Can you tell who’s the 1 year old eli & who’s the 1 year old Wolfie ? 🐒 (probably due to the baby shark hat betraying the photo 🥲) In my family we’re all about cheesy traditions but that’s what makes it special 🦋  the other respected tradition : every year since i was very little till my teenage year, I was always boubou for my birthday (i was too cool for it i think hahaha) well! We now discovered that Wolfie is the same 😂 my baby, ily happy birthday birthday girl 🎂 (don’t tell me we’ve already celebrated it, I KNOW ! But i could celebrate my baby girl 1m times tbh we do us 👉🏽👈🏽)

node.text: I just launched these new kinis on @hoaka_swimwear 😍 it’s eco friendly, made out of recycled plastic 👙♻️ we have this beautiful triangle top as well as the convertible top & the baby/kids matching swim 😋 1 top is like having 10 bikinis, it’s a good gift for the planet, plus we plant 10 trees per order 🌱 we have planted over half a million trees in less than a year because of you girls 🥺 launching tomorrow on @hoaka_swimwear 💕 ps: every details were really well thought, on each sides of the convertible top there is a comfy straight bar which make it stay in place & the straps are removable 🦋 I love creating bikinis all about the details, from the comfiest & softest fabric to the eco friendly side & the flattering fits that stay in place ✨ 4 bottom coverages available 🦩kids swims are available from 6 months to 6 years 🐒 international shipping 🌎

node.text: Neck kisses, coffee dates & midnight car rides ✨ I’m currently practicing having fun with my ownself, the car rides & coffee dates are an easy everyday for me but I have to admit I miss the neck kisses & just cuddling 🥺 I love cuddling with Doupie but I’m sure you get what I mean, it’s been such a lonnnng time I don’t even remember how it feels 🦩 (me currently fantasizing on a perfect date but also me being an introvert & never accepting any dates cause I don’t feel like dating anyway, but dating is like clubbing : you miss it till the day you finally do it to remember why you hate it)

node.text: Video dedicated for my baby girl Wolfie, I hope you will enjoy watching it when you get older so you can remember & relive those amazing moments we had together (everytime i think of the fact babies forget when they’re babies as they grow it makes me cry cause I cannot believe those moments are soooo intense for me but she won’t remember🥺) hope this video will help hihi ❤️ As you can see, you were always the most intelligent, beautiful & incredible girl, you certainly still are today (yes talking to you Wolfie of the future haha) You make everyday the most beautiful day of my life again & again & again. You have this super power of bringing everyone together & making everyone smile on a daily basis 💕 i love you mi amor , the most loved baby on the planet 🍉
